---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
import DoubleSectionHeading from '../../components/atoms/DoubleSectionHeading.astro'
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" customBackground={true} 
backgroundColor="#0a0b0c">
  <main
    id="privacy"
    class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start h-fit min-h-screen py-36 px-16 privacy"
  >
    <DoubleSectionHeading
      accentHeading="LEGAL"
      mainHeading="Privacy Policy"
      animationClass="privacy-animation"
    />

    <div class="flex flex-col items-start w-full mt-10">
      <span class="text-md text-gray-300"> Last updated: March 23, 2025</span>

      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg my-4 subtitle">1. Introduction</p>
       At INNOVAQUEST SOLUTIONS S.R.L., we respect your privacy and are
      committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains
      how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you engage our
      automation services. <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg my-4 subtitle">
        2. Information We Collect
      </p> We may collect the following types of information:

      <ol class="m-4">
        <span class='mb-4"'> Personal Information</span>
        <li>• Names and contact details of your team members</li>
        <li>• Email addresses</li>
        <li>• Business phone numbers</li>
        <li>• Job titles</li>
      </ol>
      <ol class="m-4">
        <span class='mb-4"'> Business Information</span>
        <li>• Company name and address</li>
        <li>• Business workflows and processes</li>
        <li>• System access credentials (provided for integration purposes)</li>
        <li>• Data needed to create automation solutions</li>
      </ol>
      <ol class="m-4">
        <span class='mb-4"'> Technical Information</span>
        <li>• IP addresses</li>
        <li>• Browser type and version</li>
        <li>• Access times</li>
        <li>• Pages visited on our website</li>
      </ol>

       The specific details of services provided will be outlined in your order or
      project agreement.<p class="text-gray-300 text-lg my-4 subtitle">
        How We Use Your Information
      </p>
      <ol class="m-4">
        <span class='mb-4"'> We use your information to:</span>
        <li>• Provide and maintain our services</li>
        <li>• Communicate with you about your project</li>
        <li>• Develop and test automations for your business</li>
        <li>• Improve our services</li>
        <li>• Send invoices and collect payments</li>
        <li>• Comply with legal obligations</li>
      </ol>

      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg my-4 subtitle">
        4. Data Storage and Security
      </p>
      <ul class="m-4">
        <li>
          4.1. <strong>Security Measures</strong>: We implement appropriate
          technical and organizational measures to protect your data.
        </li>
        <li>
          4.2. <strong>Data Retention</strong>: We keep your data only for as
          long as necessary to fulfill the purposes for which it was collected.
        </li>
        <li>
          4.3. <strong>Third-Party Services</strong>: When creating automations,
          we may need to integrate with third-party services. We only share the
          minimum information necessary for these integrations to function.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg my-4 subtitle">
        5. Your Data in Automations
      </p>
      <ul class="m-4">
        <li>
          5.1. <strong>Data Processing</strong>: When developing automations, we
          may process your business data to create effective workflows.
        </li>
        <li>
          5.2. <strong>Credentials</strong>: If you provide access credentials
          for your systems, we use these solely for creating and testing your
          automations.
        </li>
        <li>
          5.3. <strong>Data Ownership</strong>: You retain ownership of all your
          business data processed through our automations.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg my-4 subtitle">6. Confidentiality</p>
       We treat all information about your business processes, workflows, and
      systems as confidential. We will not share this information with third
      parties except as required to deliver our services or as required by law.

      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg my-4 subtitle">7. Cookies and Tracking</p>

       Our website may use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your
      experience and collect information about how you use our site. You can control
      cookies through your browser settings.
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg my-4 subtitle">8. Your Rights</p>
      <ol class="m-4">
        <span class='mb-4"'>
          Depending on your location, you may have the following rights
          regarding your data:</span
        >
        <li>• Access your personal information</li>
        <li>• Correct inaccurate data</li>
        <li>• Delete your data</li>
        <li>• Object to processing</li>
        <li>• Data portability</li>
        <li>• Withdraw consent</li>
      </ol>
       To exercise these rights, please contact us at office@innovaquest.ai.
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg my-4 subtitle">
        9. Updates to This Policy
      </p>
       We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. The latest version will
      always be posted on our website with the effective date.
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg my-4 subtitle">10. Contact Us</p>
      <ul class="m-4">
        If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices,
        please contact us:
        <li>• Email: office@innovaquest.ai</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
